---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
<section class="bg-[#07001C] pt-32 pb-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <span class="bg-[#110833] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.3)] text-[#7C3AED] text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Intelligence artificielle</span>
      <h1 class="font-syne font-extrabold text-[#F1F0F7] mt-4 mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);line-height:1.1;">IA appliquee a votre entreprise</h1>
      <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-lg leading-relaxed">Solutions d&#39;IA concretes pour automatiser vos taches repetitives, analyser vos donnees et augmenter la productivite.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8 flex-wrap">
        <a href="tel:+262692311191" class="bg-[#7C3AED] hover:bg-[#6D28D9] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all">Discuter de votre projet</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.4)] text-[#F1F0F7] hover:border-[#7C3AED] font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all">Nous contacter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.15)] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] mb-3">Automatisation de processus</h3>
        <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Identification et automatisation des taches repetitives : saisie, classement, rapports. Votre equipe se concentre sur ce qui a de la valeur.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.15)] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] mb-3">Chatbots et assistants</h3>
        <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Chatbot client sur votre site, assistant interne pour vos equipes. Disponible 24h/24, integre a votre Dolibarr ou CRM.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.15)] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] mb-3">Analyse de donnees</h3>
        <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Tableaux de bord intelligents, predictions de ventes, detection d&#39;anomalies — transformez vos donnees en decisions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#0A0022] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.2)] rounded-2xl p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] text-2xl mb-4">Notre approche</h2>
      <p class="text-[#9B99AA] mb-6">On identifie le cas d&#39;usage le plus impactant, on le teste a petite echelle, puis on deploie. Budget maitrise, resultat mesurable.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="text-center p-3 bg-[#0D0028] rounded-lg"><div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold text-lg">1</div><div class="text-[#9B99AA] text-xs">Atelier de cadrage</div></div>
        <div class="text-center p-3 bg-[#0D0028] rounded-lg"><div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold text-lg">2</div><div class="text-[#9B99AA] text-xs">Prototype 2 semaines</div></div>
        <div class="text-center p-3 bg-[#0D0028] rounded-lg"><div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold text-lg">3</div><div class="text-[#9B99AA] text-xs">Validation equipes</div></div>
        <div class="text-center p-3 bg-[#0D0028] rounded-lg"><div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold text-lg">4</div><div class="text-[#9B99AA] text-xs">Deploiement et formation</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.2)] rounded-xl p-6 max-w-xl">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Un cas d&#39;usage en tete ?</h3>
      <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm mb-4">Atelier de cadrage gratuit — on evalue la faisabilite et le ROI.</p>
      <a href="tel:+262692311191" class="bg-[#7C3AED] hover:bg-[#6D28D9] text-white text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-all inline-block">0692 31 11 91</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
